# Terraform Commands

- `terraform apply` - Run terraform apply with auto-approve
- `terraform destroy` - Run terraform destroy with auto-approve
- `tf init` - Initialize Terraform with plugin upgrades
- `tf plan` - Run terraform plan
- `tf capply` - Install provider and apply changes (shortcut to make capply) 